p: The rats in the CUS + OEO received essential oil of oregano (0.2 mL /kg, i.p.), CUS + fluoxetine (FLX) group was given fluoxetine (10 mg/kg, i.p. Aria Pharmaceutical Co. Iran), CUS + diazepam (DZ) rats treated with diazepam (3 mg/kg, i.p. Sobhan Darou Co. Iran) and the CUS group only supplied with saline (0.2 mL/kg, i.p.).
